Ive installed the plugin sent_confirmation-1.6-1.2 on our  
squirrelmail 1.4.10a-2~dapper1

Works fine.

Ive configured in the config.php:

    $sent_conf_message_style = 4;

and also

    $sent_conf_include_cc = 1;

(see the grep output below)

